<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../lib/bootstrap-3.3.5-dist/css/bootstrap.css">
    <style>
        .goods_footer{
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        ul{
            list-style: none;
        }
        ul> li {
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1{
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        h3{
            padding-left: 30px;
        }
        .goods_jiesao{
            margin-top: 100px;
            height: 200px;
            display: table-cell;
            vertical-align:middle;
            text-align:center;
        }
        .goods_footer_biaoti{
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer_image1{
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            height: 200px;
        }
        .footer_image1 img{
            height: 300px;
        }
        .goods_mingxing{
            text-align: center;
        }
        .goods_jiage1{
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .goods_mingxing img {
            width: 190px;
            height: 250px;
        }
        .section{
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .section>ul {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p{
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        #mingxing{
            border:#E0E0E0 solid 8px ;
            margin-top: 30px;

        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
<%- include("./common/header.ejs")%>
<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-2 col-lg-offset-2 goods_footer" >
            <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked">
                <h4><a>脸部保养</a></h4>
                <li><a href="huli">舒缓护理</a></li>
                <li><a href="huli">净化护理</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h2>男士</h2>
            <hr>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 footer_image1">
                    <img src="../images/Homme_categorie.jpg" class="col-lg-12">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-8 goods_jiesao">
                    <div>
                        通常情况下，男性肌肤自身的防御能力的确是较强，但是随着剃须形成为男性日常生活习惯后，
                        每天对男性肌肤产生的刺激和影响随之而来。法国希思黎为男士度身研发了满足男士需求的轻薄
                        且哑光质地的护肤产品，其中添加的主要活性成分气味清新自然。只需快捷，简单，有效的几个
                        步骤，男士肌肤立现健康光彩，焕发活力。
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row " id="mingxing">

                <div class="col-lg-12 goods_footer_biaoti">
                    法国希思黎明星产品
                </div>
                <%data[2].forEach((item)=>{%>
                <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                    <img src="../images/<%=item.d_smallSrc%>">
                    <div><%=item.g_name%></div>
                    <div class="goods_jiage1">明星产品</div>
                    <div class="goods_jiage1">￥<%=item.d_price%></div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn ">查看产品</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn ">快速购买</button>
                </div>
                <%})%>
            </div>
            <div class="row section">
                <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
                    <li role="presentation" class="active"><a href="#home" aria-controls="home" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">舒缓护理</a></li>
                    <li role="presentation"><a href="#profile" aria-controls="profile" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">净化护理</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div  class="col-lg-2">产品匹配您的搜索</div>
                <div class="col-lg-2 col-lg-offset-8 dropdown">
                    分类:
                    <button class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" type="button" id="dropdownMenu1" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="true">
                        价格
                        <span class="caret"></span>
                    </button>
                    <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenu1">
                        <li><a href="#">价格 低至高</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">价格 高至低</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <!-- Tab panes -->
                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane active" id="home">
                        <div class="row" id="xuanranGoods">
                            <%data[0].forEach((item)=>{%>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                                <div><img src="../images/<%=item.d_smallSrc%>"></div>
                                <p><%=item.g_name%></p>
                                <p><%=item.g_descript%></p>
                                <p>￥<%=item.d_price%></p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn ">查看产品</button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn ">快速购买</button>
                            </div>
                            <%})%>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="profile">
                        <div class="row" id="xuanranGoods">
                            <%data[1].forEach((item)=>{%>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                                <div><img src="../images/<%=item.d_smallSrc%>"></div>
                                <p><%=item.g_name%></p>
                                <p><%=item.g_descript%></p>
                                <p>￥<%=item.d_price%></p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn ">查看产品</button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn ">快速购买</button>
                            </div>
                            <%})%>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<%- include("./common/footer.ejs")%>
<script src="../lib/bootstrap-3.3.5-dist/js/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
<script src="../lib/bootstrap-3.3.5-dist/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
<script>
</script>
</body>
</html>